				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Most games with battery save use some kind of trivial checksum/CRC. I've never heard of anyone having found any evidence of error recovery.<br /><br />I've been meaning to write a BCH-21/31 forward-error correction implementation for the NES for a while, but I don't know whether it would help with battery save corruption.</div>

