it on the first time.<br />Nah, in this case, the save state will be treated as empty.<br /><br />Also, in this case, I can simply delete a savestate by setting its hash value to 0. There would be no distinction between &quot;valid, but empty state&quot; and &quot;empty state because it's invalid&quot;.<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle">Pokun wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">An option to manually wipe the save data is also nice to have so you don't have to rip out the battery.</div><br />Sure, this will be part of the game anyway.</div>

					
